# Home Assistant add-ons run as root under the Supervisor by design — the
# Supervisor manages isolation, and bashio/s6 need root. Not a real finding here.
AVD-DS-0002
# No HEALTHCHECK in the Dockerfile — the Supervisor watchdog handles add-on
# liveness (startup: application / boot: auto), so a container HEALTHCHECK is moot.
AVD-DS-0026
